# FraudShield — Full Stack Audit Report

> **Audit Date:** 25 Feb 2026 · **Auditor:** Antigravity AI  
> **State:** MVP live on `api.fraudshieldprotect.com` · `npm run dev` + `flutter run` both active

---

## 1. Executive Summary

| Dimension | Grade | Notes |
|-----------|:-----:|-------|
| **Security** | B+ | All S1–S10 done. Email verification + flutter_secure_storage outstanding |
| **Backend Architecture** | B | Clean Express/Prisma structure. Missing rewards route, mock email service |
| **Frontend Architecture** | B+ | 43 screens, solid API service with token refresh & cert pinning |
| **Data Integrity** | B | Risk engine works, but phone detection still crowdsource-only |
| **Reliability** | B- | No CI/CD, 1 test file, no Swagger docs |
| **Feature Completeness** | A- | 13/17 core features real. 4 stubs correctly hidden |
| **Rollup Readiness** | ✅ **Yes — with 5 must-fix items** | See §5 below |

---

## 2. Backend Audit

### ✅ What's Working Well

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **Middleware stack** | `helmet` + `cors` + `compression` + `morgan→Winston` + `requestTimeout(30s)` all wired correctly in [app.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/app.ts) |
| **Auth** | JWT (15m) + refresh (30d) rotation, `passport-jwt`, rate limiting (`authLimiter`, `loginLimiter`), change-password requires `currentPassword` |
| **Risk Engine** | [RiskEvaluationService](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/services/risk-evaluation.service.ts#23-223) — 4-factor weighted scoring (community reports 35%, verification ratio 30%, reporter rep 20%, recency 15%), logarithmic curve, well-commented |
| **Alert Engine** | Real FCM dispatch via `firebase-admin`, Haversine distance calc, Redis dedup (1 alert/user/category/day for trending, 1/hour for local) |
| **Scam Report** | Full CRUD + soft verification, geo-indexed, paginated, search with filters |
| **Rewards** | [rewards.controller.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/controllers/rewards.controller.ts) (17 KB) and related routes wired through [feature.routes.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/routes/feature.routes.ts) |
| **Transaction Journal** | PHONE/BANK/DOC categories, journal→scam report conversion |
| **DB Performance** | Indexes on ScamReport, unique constraint on Verification, `limit=50` cap on risk eval query |
| **Infra** | Nginx + Let's Encrypt, Docker Compose prod, healthcheck, pinned versions, log rotation, DB backups |
| **Logging** | Winston structured logging, morgan → Winston in production, error handler excludes req.body |

### ⚠️ Issues Found

| Severity | ID | Finding | File | Fix |
|:--------:|-----|---------|------|-----|
| 🔴 | B1 | **Mock email service** — OTP logged to `console.log`, never actually sent to user. Password reset only works in dev if you read logs | `src/services/email.service.ts:35-38` | Integrate Nodemailer + SMTP (or Brevo/SendGrid free tier). ~2 hrs |
| 🟠 | B2 | **`rewards.routes.ts` is commented out** in [app.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/app.ts) line 20, 107 — comment says "File missing" but [rewards.controller.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/controllers/rewards.controller.ts) exists (17 KB). Route is unreachable at `/api/v1/rewards` | `src/app.ts:20` | Create `src/routes/rewards.routes.ts` and uncomment |
| 🟠 | B3 | **`console.log` in [alert-engine.service.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/services/alert-engine.service.ts)** (9 occurrences) — production logs bypass Winston | `src/services/alert-engine.service.ts:106,112,126,189,198,262` | Replace with `logger.info/error` |
| 🟠 | B4 | **Phone check still community-only** — [semak-mule.service.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/services/semak-mule.service.ts) exists and CCID research is done but `RiskEvaluationService.evaluate()` doesn't call it | [src/services/risk-evaluation.service.ts](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/services/risk-evaluation.service.ts) | Wire Semak Mule lookup into [evaluate()](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/src/services/risk-evaluation.service.ts#32-86) for type=`phone` |
| 🟡 | B5 | **No Swagger/OpenAPI docs** — 14 controllers, zero documentation | — | Integrate `swagger-jsdoc` + `swagger-ui-express` |
| 🟡 | B6 | **Only 1 test file** (auth controller) — 13 other controllers untested | `tests/` | Add tests for report, rewards, transaction controllers |
| 🟡 | B7 | **No CI/CD pipeline** — deployments are manual `git pull` + docker restart | — | Add GitHub Actions workflow |
| 🟡 | B8 | **DB connection pooling not configured** — default Prisma pool may be insufficient under load | `src/config/database.ts` | Add `connection_limit` to DATABASE_URL or Prisma datasource |
| 🟡 | B9 | **Soft delete on ScamReport not implemented** — reports are hard-deleted | — | Add `deletedAt DateTime?` field and filter in queries |
| 🟡 | B10 | **`firebase-admin` SDK JSON file committed to repo** ([fraudshield-271b0-firebase-adminsdk-fbsvc-2a70150a06.json](file:///c:/Fraudshield/fraudshield-backend/fraudshield-271b0-firebase-adminsdk-fbsvc-2a70150a06.json)) | repo root | Move to env var `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT` as JSON string |

