## 5. Can We Roll Up? Feature Rollup Readiness

> **Short answer: YES — with 5 must-fix items before marketing/scaling**

### Core Feature Status for Rollup

| Feature | Real? | Rollup-Safe? | Blocker? |
|---------|:-----:|:------------:|:--------:|
| Fraud Check (Phone/URL/Bank/Doc) | ⚠️ Partial | ✅ | Phone still heuristic — don't advertise as "CCID verified" yet |
| QR Scanner | ⚠️ Basic | ✅ | Acceptable for MVP |
| Scam Reporting | ✅ Real | ✅ | — |
| Community Feed + Verification | ✅ Real | ✅ | — |
| Transaction Journal | ✅ Real | ✅ | — |
| Subscription System | ⚠️ No payment gateway | ⚠️ | Cannot charge users until B paygate wired (Phase 4) |
| Rewards / Points Store | ✅ Real | ✅ | Rewards route unreachable (B2) — fix first |
| Scam Map | ✅ Real | ✅ | — |
| Badge System | ✅ Real | ✅ | — |
| User Auth | ✅ Real | ⚠️ | Email verification mock (B1/F3) — fix before big user push |
| Push Notifications | ✅ Partial | ✅ | FCM dispatch exists, subscriber flow works. Not marketed yet. |
| Voice Detection | 🚫 Hidden | ✅ | Correctly gated |
| Transaction Risk Alerts | 🚫 Mock | ✅ | Correctly marked as mock, not marketed |

### The 5 Must-Fix Items Before Scaling

| # | Priority | Item | Est. |
|---|----------|------|------|
| 1 | 🔴 | **B1: Real email service** — password reset is broken in production | 2 hrs |
| 2 | 🔴 | **B2: Re-add rewards route** — `/api/v1/rewards` is 404 | 30 min |
| 3 | 🟠 | **F1: flutter_secure_storage** — token security before wider user base | 1 hr |
| 4 | 🟠 | **B4: Wire Semak Mule** — make phone check genuinely real | 3 hrs |
| 5 | 🟠 | **F9: Fix Google Sign-In hang** — auth flow broken for Google users | 2 hrs |

### When to Scale Marketing

```
Rollup gate:  ✅ Fix items 1–5 above  (~8 hrs work)
Growth gate:  Phase 4 payment gateway + B3/F4/F7/F8 cleanup (~25 hrs)
Scale gate:   CI/CD + tests + BM localization + Swagger (~15 hrs)
```

